* docs for validators
* javascript context reconstruction ( deserialize the result of
  json.dumps( context ) to a javascript obj which should behave
  similar to Context )
* validators as parameters
* (propably) remove pre_validate, post_validate, fieldset
  - using pre and post_validate is exactly the same as using &
  - defining a Schema with a fieldset is exactly the same as using
    mySchema = Schema( 'field1', Validator(), 'field2', Validator())
* unit tests
